::Switchblade/Astroblast/Drag Strip/Dead-End/Rippersnapper::
Switchblade watched the procedure with intrest, he chuckles to 
himself, <Beastbox is ruthless> as he sees Megatron put the 
suction cup thingy on Condor's head, he wonders. "Megs, Yo 
Megs, what is the suction thingy ya got there?"

Astroblast, Dead-End and Drag Strip have finished putting all of the 
salvaged parts into the ship. "Megatron, this is Astroblast, we have 
finished putting all of the the savaged parts into the ship, what now 
needs to be done now?"

Rippersnapper feels Sinnertwin's bite, and roars. He tries to ram 
his head into Sinnertwin's stomach.
